---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home" description="Max Weiner — Customer Success, AI, Builder">

  <div class="mw-hero">
    <div class="mw-hero-tag">Customer Success · AI · Doer</div>
    <h1 class="mw-hero-headline">Max Weiner<br><em>[ tagline ]</em></h1>
  </div>

  <div class="mw-hook">
    <div class="mw-hook-lines">
      <p class="mw-hook-line">Ten years ago I got laid off and went to Vegas to "figure things out."</p>
      <p class="mw-hook-line">Last week, I got back from Vegas for a bachelor party.</p>
      <p class="mw-hook-line">I got laid off again on Thursday.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mw-narrative">
    <div class="mw-narrative-rule"></div>
    <p>
      Some things change. At 25, Vegas was a week of wandering through casino food courts on a Wednesday afternoon wondering what came next. This time I had a king bed, great shows, and spent most of it counting down to get home to my sons. Progress, maybe.
    </p>
    <p>
      What hasn't changed: I still don't have a clean answer to what comes next. I have <strong>seven months of severance</strong>, a newborn, a toddler, a dog named Loki, and a list of things I've been meaning to build, write, and think about. This site is where I do that out loud.
    </p>
    <div class="pullquote">
      The company told me I'd helped build a better Internet.<br>Turns out the Internet didn't need as much help as they thought.
    </div>
    <p>
      I've spent ten years in <strong>Customer Success</strong> — at startups, at a public company, most recently at Cloudflare. I care about the function deeply, especially now that AI is eating the repetitive surface of it and forcing everyone to figure out what actually matters. I have opinions about that. Some of them will end up here.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm also a <strong>CS career coach</strong>, a tinkerer, a Michigan football fan with bad opinions about Big Ten expansion, and someone who moved to Barcelona on a whim and came back right as COVID started. This site will have some of that too.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here's what to expect: a build log, some essays, a resume with a chatbot trained on me, and an archived version of the 2019 site I built for a grad school marketing class that somehow included a lasagna recipe. Explore in whichever order makes sense.
    </p>
    <div class="mw-nav-site">
      <a href="/about">About me</a>
      <a href="/the-work">The Work</a>
      <a href="/work-with-me">Work With Me</a>
      <a href="/archive">The Archive</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mw-interactive-placeholder">
    <div class="mw-placeholder-label">Interactive element — TBD</div>
    <p class="mw-placeholder-desc">Something fun lives here. Timeline, bingo card, quiz, contrast card.<br>To be decided.</p>
  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Override Layout's main constraints so sections control their own spacing */
  :global(main) {
    max-width: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .mw-hero {
    padding: 5.5rem 3rem 3rem;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  .mw-hero-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

.mw-hero-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-ubuntu);
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .mw-hero-headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .mw-hook {
    padding: 2.5rem 3rem 0;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .mw-hook-lines {
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .mw-hook-line {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #3A3A36;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.2rem 0;
  }

  .mw-hook-line strong {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .mw-hook-line.muted {
    color: #7A7A72;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .mw-narrative {
    padding: 3rem 3rem 0;
    max-width: 660px;
  }

  .mw-narrative-rule {
    width: 48px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .mw-narrative p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #4A4A44;
    margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .mw-narrative p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .mw-narrative strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .mw-narrative em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #3A3A36;
  }

  .pullquote {
    font-family: var(--font-ubuntu);
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin: 1.75rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .mw-nav-site {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .mw-nav-site a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .mw-nav-site a::after {
    content: '→';
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .mw-interactive-placeholder {
    margin: 4rem 3rem;
    border: 1.5px dashed rgba(26, 58, 107, 0.25);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    background: rgba(26, 58, 107, 0.02);
  }

  .mw-placeholder-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .mw-placeholder-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #9A9A90;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
